initial_wakeup_prompt:
It is {current_time} on {current_date}. The weather at {location} is {weather_description}. A summary of my daily schedule and ongoing tasks follows:

{daily_summary}

Write a friendly morning wakeup which prepares me for the day. Mention the time and weather, one or two concise highlights from my schedule, and include an inspirational quote to start the week off right.

snooze_wakeup_prompt:
It is {current_time} on {current_date}; my requested wakeup time was {wakeup_time} and I have snoozed {snooze_count} times. The weather at {location} is {weather_description}. A summary of my daily schedule and ongoing tasks follows:

{daily_summary}

Write an appropriately insistent wakeup message which urges me to get and and prepares me for the day. Highlight the current time and when I was meant to wake up and one or two concise highlights from my schedule. The tone should be friendly but firm.
